OL,3,CBenefits law 'breaches human rights'
OL,4,Cafter man is denied pension
OL,6,FMark's daughter Meg has severe autism,
OL,7,Fand his son Ryan has downs syndrome.
OL,9,FBoth children will never be able to
OL,10,Fhave full time employment.
OL,12,FHe says at the moment financially they
OL,13,Fare "just about coping", but the extra
OL,14,Fmoney from his pension would make a
OL,15,Fhuge difference at a time when costs
OL,16,Fare going up.
OL,18,F"For 32 years I worked at the same
OL,19,Faccountancy practice, so I was paying
OL,20,Fa significant contribution", he says.
