OL,3,CBenefits law 'breaches human rights'
OL,4,Cafter man is denied pension
OL,6,F"My employer was paying six and half
OL,7,Fpercent of my salary and I was paying
OL,8,Fin six - so there was what I would say
OL,9,Fwas quite a lot in my pot.
OL,11,F"So when I found out I wasn't entitled
OL,12,Fto it I thought it just can't be
OL,13,Fright."
OL,15,FMark first raised the issue with the
OL,16,Fthen Social Security Minister back in
OL,17,F2021, when he started a petition which
OL,18,Fgot more than 1000 signatures - but
OL,19,Fsince then, nothing has changed.
