OL,3,CBenefits law 'breaches human rights'
OL,4,Cafter man is denied pension
OL,6,FHe's decided to raise the issue again
OL,7,Fby putting in a formal complaint to
OL,8,FDeputy Lyndsay Feltham, the island's
OL,9,Fcurrent Social Security Minister.
OL,11,FMark says the law is archaic and needs
OL,12,Fto change.
OL,14,F"It's heart breaking - you care out of
OL,15,Flove and you'll never stop doing it,
OL,16,Fand you do think you're put on
OL,17,Fsometimes," he says, "but I know 100
OL,18,Fpercent that if something happened to
OL,19,Fme now and I couldn't care for Ryan
OL,20,Fand Meg it would cost the state around
OL,21,F#300,000 a year."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
