OL,3,CBenefits law 'breaches human rights'
OL,4,Cafter man is denied pension
OL,6,F"It's about time we followed Guernsey
OL,7,Fon this - and I hate to say this as a
OL,8,FJerseyman, but Guernsey got it right
OL,9,Fand we got it wrong."
OL,11,FHe adds: "You work till retirement
OL,12,Fage, you pay into the system, you need
OL,13,Fa lot of years of contributions to get
OL,14,Fa full pension, and then they deny it
OL,15,Fto you, and yet the cost to the tax
OL,16,Fpayer, the cost to the States, in this
OL,17,Fcase if Mark didn't look after his
OL,18,Fadult children, would be enormous."
OL,20,FKey allegations that Mark has made in
OL,21,Fhis formal complaint:
