OL,3,CBenefits law 'breaches human rights'
OL,4,Cafter man is denied pension
OL,6,FMark is calling for an overhaul of the
OL,7,Fcurrent benefits law, including the
OL,8,Fimmediate suspension of the 1975
OL,9,FOverlapping Benefits Law.
OL,11,FHe wants Jersey to follow Guernsey's
OL,12,Flead and allow carers to receive both
OL,13,Ftheir carers benefits and their old
OL,14,Fage pension - saying the government
OL,15,Fneeds to recognise that caregiving
OL,16,Fcontinues even when someone is retired
OL,17,For unable to work.
OL,19,FITV has asked the Social Security
OL,20,FMinister for a response.
